  "exportCopyTitle": "A copy of all your data",
  "exportDescriptionBody": "A JSON file with all profiles, medications, schedule, doses, wellbeing logs, and doctor visits — everything stored on this device. You can open it anywhere or share it with anyone.\n\nMedication photos are not included in the file (they're already in your \"Backup\") — text data only.",
